==Prayer AFK Area==
*When you reach Darkmeyer using Drakan's Medallion, run north to the Bank area. There is a Bank and an [[Statue (Darkmeyer)|Altar]], you can save money with the method of praying at the altar and avoid using Prayer potions. Activate "Protect from melee" and fight the vyrewatch. When you reach low prayer points, pray at the altar.
*To use the bank you have to bring your Vyre noble costume, put them on when you want to deposit any item, or withdraw super combat sets.
*You may want to collect the Vampyre dust for use at the Hallowed Sepulchre.
*You may also opt for a [[Ring of wealth|Ring of Wealth]] since these monsters regularly drop up to 1500 coins.






